extends ./shared/layout

block main
    .container#VENDORS
        .outer-container
            .inner-container
                
                p.font-red Anyone interested in becoming a vendor should email 
                    | <a href='mailto:phxveganfest@gmail.com'>phxveganfest@gmail.com</a> for an application. 
                
                .text-picture
                    .text
                        p Reach an audience of more than 2,000-targeted consumers who are looking to support the 
                            | vegan community! PHX Vegan Food Festival attendees are passionate about living a 
                            | vegan lifestyle and are looking for local businesses that offer vegan and vegan-friendly 
                            | food and products. 
                    .picture
                        img(src='/vendor-generic.jpg', alt='vendor image')
                    .clearfix
                    
                br
                
                h2 Vendors
                p Vendors will be provided a 10x10 booth to showcase their goods and 
                    | services. You may sample and/or sell items. We are looking for restaurants, 
                    | food and beverage products, household items, personal care items, clothing 
                    | and accessories.
                h4.no-bottom-margin VIP Swag Bags
                p.no-top-margin Reach a select audience at the PHX Vegan Food Festival by having a 
                    | sample of your product showcased in our VIP goody bags. 
                    | A minimum of 400 samples is required.
                    
                h2 Presenters
                p During the PHX Vegan Food Festival, we offer a full day of 
                    | entertainment for our guests. We are seeking vegan chefs and cookbook 
                    | authors, health and fitness experts, horticulturalists, and more to 
                    | demo recipes or provide a presentation during the festival.
                    
                br
                
                h2 Phoenix Vegan Food Festival Demos & Discussions
                p.small-container.center We are planning on showcasing live vegan cooking 
                    | demonstrations and informative discussions and lectures.
                p.small-container.center Visit this page as we get closer to February 25, 2017
                    | to see the list of amazing chefs, trainers, and vegans
                    | that are here to educate and entertain!
                    
